mke:Activity rdfs:comment "A unit of work within a workflow, comprised of one or more tasks." .
mke:Challenge rdfs:comment "A difficulty or obstacle faced by practitioners when adopting or implementing a set of practices." .
mke:SearchString rdfs:comment "A query expression used to retrieve potentially relevant items from a search system." .
mke:DataExtraction rdfs:label "Data extraction" .
mke:ResearchQuestion a owl:Class .
